# as $VAR in the output, see render-config.sh) are substituted at render time.
# Supported variables (allowlisted in ../render-config.sh):
#   HOST_IP      - host IP for Redis / Kafka / headerless endpoints (required)
#   NUM_STREAMS  - optional, propagated through if referenced
#
# Regenerate config.yml after editing this file:
#   HOST_IP=10.57.202.234 ../render-config.sh

